description: This is the checksum for the second half of the Port B EDID.  This is calculated automatically.

data.name: uSpaLocation

data.name: uKsvListReady

written into the Repeater Map.  The system must also set bits [11:0] of Bstatus before setting this bit.

data.name: uSpaLocationMsb
description: Additional MSB of SPA_location  (i.e. spa_location[8]) needed to point to SPAs stored in second segment.
